		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Can the Snes be reset from the game cartridge?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In that case it should be much easier. Use a simple on/off switch, connect one pin to MAD-1 Pin 9 (/RESET) and the middle pin to ground.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


